headline: POOPH® Cites Quality-Control Issues in Supplier Termination
summary: POOPH®, Inc. terminated ONM, one of its suppliers and a subsidiary of BioLargo Inc., pursuant to Section 8.2(b) of the parties' contract, due to ONM's failure to deliver products as required under their agreement.
